---
title: King Prawn and Sweet Potato Korma Style Curry with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Basmati Rice
description: A customer favourite, this King Prawn and Sweet Potato Korma Style Curry is a tried-and-tested recipe that always wins with a crowd.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R340_W23_UK_C3951-22655-16_Main_low-5d61e086.jpg
